{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"94811a8cf1","title":"给王梓木“的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9e4c7caf4b","index":0,"year":1945,"month":3,"day":2,"articleId":"94811a8cf1"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji19","name":"毛泽东全集第19卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji19.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji19":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"affcc7c97d","type":"paragraph","text":"给王梓木“的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"94811a8cf1"},{"id":"a1e9f9903e","type":"paragraph","text":"（1945年3月2日）梓木同志：来信看到了。欢迎你回来。你过去做了许多有益于党与人民的工作，今后望你继续做下去。一时的错误你已改正了，了解了，也就过去了，不要时时记在心里。也许你经过这个挫折会要大进一步的，那么，错误也就转变为有益了同志的敬礼！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"94811a8cf1"},{"id":"ee61ff4ae2","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"94811a8cf1"},{"id":"49403c6ee4","type":"paragraph","text":"三月二日[1]王梓木（1895-1969），黑龙江木兰人。1925年加入中国共产党，后长期被派在国民党军队中工作。抗日战争爆发后在武汉、重庆等地假","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"94811a8cf1"}],"page":{"id":"aa6cda3b60","publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"94811a8cf1","start":345,"end":345}}}},"__N_SSG":true}